---
import sewing from "../assets/sewing.jpg";
---

<div id="about" class="bg-[#FFF9F3] px-8 py-20 md:py-32 lg:px-24">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center space-y-10">
    <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-serif text-gray-900 tracking-tight">
      About Us
    </h1>
    <div class="space-y-6 text-lg md:text-xl text-gray-700 leading-relaxed font-light">
      <p>
        Loom is a sewing studio focused on quality, simplicity, and precision.
        We create well-crafted textile pieces using thoughtful design and
        careful attention to detail.
      </p>

      <p>
        Our work is rooted in craftsmanship and durability, combining
        traditional sewing techniques with a modern, minimal approach. Every
        piece is made with intention, valuing both function and form.
      </p>

      <p class="font-medium text-gray-900 pt-4">
        At Loom, we believe in timeless design and textiles made to last.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div title="image" class="w-[400px] h-[400px] flex justify-center items-center">
      <img src={sewing.src} alt="loom" class="w-full h-full object-cover rounded-lg shadow-xl shadow-black/10 transform transition duration-500 hover:scale-[1.02]"/>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
